nodes.text: A skirmish took place in the starship Radiant IX on the asteroid Poison Moon in the Hoth system, between Jedi Knights Et Rex and Obi-Wan Kenobi, Jedi Padawan Anakin Skywalker, and the Dark Jedi Alysun Celz. Celz was incapacitated by the Jedi, and brought back to Coruscant to stand trial for the crimes she had committed.
